Form.name: Tenant-Information Form
Form.Description: Tenant Information Form for when Tenant Management is enabled

FormElement.FormElementInstructionalText: Please select the tenant to which you want to order this service for.

Retrieval.SQLQuery: Select Min(TMEnabled) as TMEnabled from ((Select ActivateTM as TMEnabled from AcAccountConfiguration Where PrimaryID = (Select AccountConfigurationID From AcTenant where TenantID = 'ProviderBusinessTenant')) UNION (Select TenantRelevant as TMEnabled from DefService Where ServiceID = #ServiceForm.ServiceId#)) as TempTable

Rule.name: ShowNameField
Rule.Description: Rule to show tenant name field and make it mandatory based on if TM is activated

Rule.name: HideNameField
Rule.Description: Rule to hide tenant name field and make it optional based on if TM is not activated

Retrieval.SQLQuery: SELECT ShortName FROM XtrCloudConnectionInfo WHERE PrimaryID = (SELECT CASE WHEN (CloudConnectionID IS NULL OR CloudConnectionID = 0) THEN ICFDConnectionID ELSE CloudConnectionID END FROM SiUCSDVM WHERE Name = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.Name#)
SELECT DISTINCT pg.PortGroupIdentity FROM StPortGroupNames pg WHERE pg.PortGroupName = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.PortGroupName#
SELECT OwnerDataTypeID FROM SiUCSDVM WHERE Name = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.Name#

SELECT container.ContainerID FROM SiUCSDAPICContainer container JOIN SiUCSDVM vm ON container.PrimaryID = vm.OwnerID JOIN MdrDataType mdt ON vm.OwnerDataTypeID = mdt.DataTypeID AND mdt.LogicName = 'SiUCSDAPICContainer' WHERE vm.Name = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.Name#
SELECT Name FROM UdUCSDNetworkInfo WHERE OwnerID = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operatin_Action.ContainerPrimaryID# AND OwnerDataTypeID = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operatin_Action.ContainerTypeID#
SELECT epg.Label, epg.OwnerID FROM UdUCSDAPICEndpointGroup epg JOIN SiUCSDVM vm ON epg.PrimaryID = vm.APICContainerEndpointGroup WHERE vm.Name = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.Name#

SELECT epg.Label FROM UdUCSDAPICEndpointGroup epg WHERE epg.Type = 'Isolated' AND epg.ParentNetwork = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.VMNetworkName# AND epg.OwnerID = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.EpgContainerID#

SELECT DISTINCT pg.PortGroupName FROM StPortGroupNames pg JOIN UdUCSDNetworkInterface ni ON pg.PortGroupName = ni.Name JOIN SiUCSDVM vm ON vm.PrimaryID = ni.OwnerID WHERE vm.Name = #UCSD_VM_NIC_Operation_Action.Name#
